<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>9glenda</title><link>http://9glenda.github.io/</link><description>Recent content on 9glenda</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 31 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="http://9glenda.github.io/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Own Website</title><link>http://9glenda.github.io/posts/own-website/</link><pubDate>Thu, 03 Nov 2022 07:52:41 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://9glenda.github.io/posts/own-website/</guid><description>Create own website with hugo and github-pages A friend asked me about how I created this website and therefor I decided to create this small guide.
